text: Grande-Rivière Château is a commune in the Jura department in Bourgogne- Franche-Comté in eastern France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Grande-Rivière (the seat) and Château-des- Prés.Arrêté préfectoral 13 December 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Jura department ==References== * INSEE statistics Category:Communes of Jura (department)
title: Grande-Rivière Château
